description: "A navigation map of part of the north coast of Java, featuring the ports of Batavia (Jakarta) and Bantam (Serang). Includes colourful paintings of a ‘menschen fressers [cannibal]’ island, Javanese people and palm trees (dates, banana, coconut)."
title: "Particular-see-charte der Strass Sunda, nebst denen darinnen befindlichen insulen und Sandbäncken / J.W. Heydt del. ; A. Hoffer sculps."
